{
  "stem": "4963.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I would say that, you see, the-- the Lithuanians were nice to us because my mother really never had an enemy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She was always, you know, she was very kind and very good-natured and always believed that-- that you never fight with anyone, you never argue because you have two losers.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If you make peace, you have two winners, and that was her philosophy in life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was never any-- any harm done to us or any animosity towards my family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And to this day when I went back, they-- everyone said, well, who doesn't know the Ceitlin and then the Taft family, you know, with admiration?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my uncle set up practice right away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He got an apartment since he was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was a dentist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they started getting-- the Lithuanians were just flocking in to them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They took you in?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You stayed with them?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, and my-- my-- my aunt and uncle said this family wanted to keep me and they said, stay with us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We'll send you to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We'll do-- you know, we'll educate you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my uncle said, no, whatever's left of us, we have to stay together.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I left a week later or so and I went to live with my aunt and uncle Taft.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I, again, education, since it was foremost in our home, I immediately enrolled in-- in a school, in a gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I skipped all the years that I did not go to school because I insisted that I'm not going to go back in where the children are.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm going to go-- I mean, where I-- where I belong from an educational level.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I-- I wanted to be in my chronological age group.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
